data.description: Roomy one bedroom condo in the Heart of Gulf Shores! This 2nd Floor Corner unit can sleep 6 comfortably. It boasts an updated kitchen with beautiful white quartz countertops, a full-sized washing machine / dryer, and luxury vinyl flooring.  The unit is located on the end of the building offering a very private balcony with a gorgeous view of an oversized oak tree and swimming pool.  This unit has been recently remodeled with every space utilized including an extremely functional built-in bunk beds with additional storage.  Location is everything: walking distance to Gulf Shores’ Waterway District including Big Beach Brewery, Foam Coffee, Isla Wine, Tacky Jacks, A Specialty Bakery, and so much! *** A quick 10-minute drive to Gulf Shores White Sandy Beaches. *** The unit is perfect for a first-time home buyer, 2nd Home, or an Investment Property.  Do not miss this opportunity to own in Gulf Shores.
